About City Park

City Park solves the problems of parking in big cities by providing the most convenient and highly functional parking systems with the world’s best technology and most experiences. Based on the long history of experiences and know-how, City Park Tech creates comfortable & pleasant parking environment by providing various parking systems complete with high standards of safety, durability and quickness.

Annual Maintenance Contract

City Park’s dedicated maintenance department provides service to users under a comprehensive warranty or an Annual Maintenance Contract.

We provide onsite maintenance with our dedicated team of technicians and engineers visiting the site in the maintenance vans to address any concerns or requirements.

We believe in delivering quality service with standards unmatched in the industry. City park also offers emergency breakdown services 24/7 under the annual maintenance contract at no extra cost. In case of any emergency complaint, our representatives will reach the destination within 3 hours.
